  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this cohort study is to collect prospectively clinical data on all the patients
      admitted in the investigators department for bariatric surgery or for any complication of a
      bariatric procedure. The investigators goal is not only to improve the follow-up but also to
      assess and publish the investigators results regarding weight loss and the complication rate.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
